Package ohos.ivihardware.vehiclecontrol.model

Provides abstract classes about vehicle control callback and basic data types.

This package is used together with ohos.ivihardware.vehiclecontrol, providing information about property setting callback, property subscription callback, subscription filter types, and property data structure.

Since:
1
  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    VehicleActuatorCallback
    A callback class pertaining to setting a specified vehicle signal property.
    VehicleSignalCallback
    A callback class pertaining to subscribing to a specified vehicle signal property.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    PropertyInfo
    Describes vehicle signal property information.
    SubscriberFilter
    Provides a filter for subscription callback so that the callback is called only when the filter criteria are met.
    VsSubscription
    Provides information about vehicle signal properties, including the vehicle signal property path, physical zone ID, and subscription filter.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    PropertyInfo.PropertyDataType
    Enumerates data types of the vehicle signal property.
    PropertyInfo.PropertyType
    Enumerates node types of the vehicle signal property.
